https://www.balena.io/etcher
https://www.raspberrypi.com/software/operating-systems/

Pomocou etchera flashnem os image na SD kartu.
nahodit na kartu

na karte v priecinku /boot vytvorim prazdny subor bez pripony ssh aby sme povolili ssh

ak sa pripajam cez wifi vytvorim subor s nazvom wpa_supplicant.conf

country=SK
ctrl_interface=DIR=/var/run/wpa_supplicant GROUP=netdev
update_config=1

network={
    ssid="NazovVasejSiete"
    psk="HesloVasejSiete"
}

svoj public ssh kluc skopiruj do /home/pi/.ssh/authorized_keys

sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get upgrade


